@[simp] theorem gcd_gcd_self_left_left (m n : Nat) : gcd (gcd m n) m = gcd m n := by
  rw [gcd_comm m n, gcd_gcd_self_left_right]
theorem gcd_add_mul_self (m n k : Nat) : gcd m (n + k * m) = gcd m n := by
  simp [gcd_rec m (n + k * m), gcd_rec m n]
